{"iti52:0.1":"Itivuttaka 52 ","iti52:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti52:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti52:0.4":"Pathamavedanasutta ","iti52:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti52:2.1":"“Tisso ima, bhikkhave, vedana. ","iti52:2.2":"Katama tisso? ","iti52:2.3":"Sukha vedana, dukkha vedana, adukkhamasukha vedana—","iti52:2.4":"ima kho, bhikkhave, tisso vedana”ti. ","iti52:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti52:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti52:3.1":"“Samahito sampajano, ","iti52:3.2":"sato buddhassa savako; ","iti52:3.3":"Vedana ca pajanati, ","iti52:3.4":"vedanananca sambhavam. ","iti52:4.1":"Yattha ceta nirujjhanti, ","iti52:4.2":"magganca khayagaminam; ","iti52:4.3":"Vedananam khaya bhikkhu, ","iti52:4.4":"nicchato parinibbuto”ti. ","iti52:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti52:5.2":"Tatiyam. "}